<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Impact Story - AgriLinkHub</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  <div class="container">
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="page-hero-copy">
        <span class="eyebrow">Impact Stories</span>
        <h1>Stories of change from farms and communities</h1>
        <p>Discover how AgriLinkHub creates measurable results for farmers while improving livelihoods, food security, and local business growth.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="page-hero-image">
        <img src="/images/garden-maize.svg" alt="People in the garden growing maize">
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-panel">
      <h2>Our impact approach</h2>
      <p>We combine modern farm support, verified inputs, and market connections to create positive outcomes for farmers and communities. Every program is guided by data, local feedback, and measurable performance indicators.</p>
      <ul class="impact-story-list">
        <li>Assess local needs and prioritize farmer groups</li>
        <li>Deploy tailored inputs and training programs</li>
        <li>Track results using yield, income, and food security metrics</li>
        <li>Share outcomes with donors and community leaders</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section-panel">
      <h2>Quantitative impact</h2>
      <div class="impact-grid">
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>3,200+</h3>
          <p>Smallholder farmers reached through training and supply services.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>32%</h3>
          <p>Average yield increase observed after follow-up support.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>28%</h3>
          <p>Average growth in farmer household income from improved market access.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>420+</h3>
          <p>Farmers supported with access to credit, inputs, and advisory services.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-panel">
      <h2>Qualitative impact</h2>
      <ul class="impact-story-list">
        <li>"Our cooperative now uses the milled grain to supply local buyers with consistent quality."</li>
        <li>"We feel more confident selling maize at the right time, thanks to the market connections we gained."</li>
        <li>"Training on record keeping helped me manage farm expenses and increase profit."</li>
        <li>"The new inputs were easy to use and helped my crops survive dry spells."</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section-panel">
      <h2>Featured story: Kato's maize farm</h2>
      <p>Kato joined AgriLinkHub in early 2025. He received a planting plan, certified seed, and input support. His maize productivity rose by 40%, and he sold to a regional buyer for the first time. Kato now reinvests earnings into irrigation equipment and school fees for his children.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section-panel">
      <h2>Impact by category</h2>
      <div class="impact-grid">
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>Productivity</h3>
          <p>Improved crop yields and reduced post-harvest losses through better agronomy and processing tools.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>Income</h3>
          <p>Stronger revenue streams from better pricing, market linkages, and value-added processing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>Knowledge</h3>
          <p>Greater farm resilience driven by training in soil health, pest control, and crop planning.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-card">
          <h3>Community</h3>
          <p>More stable livelihoods and new opportunities for youth and women in farming communities.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>